{"tid":2101874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民黨造勢 吳靄儀籲港人勇敢行出來","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:04:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"372e118879be8c40ef75c9fcd7d2e09ba97f6730","tid":2101874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/UZ5FNTGAQK3QUXCYWWFDXDFJKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FUZ5FNTGAQK3QUXCYWWFDXDFJKI%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=acffe72f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FUZ5FNTGAQK3QUXCYWWFDXDFJKI%2F&h=287babff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/UZ5FNTGAQK3QUXCYWWFDXDFJKI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公民黨造勢 吳靄儀籲港人勇敢行出來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uMZKtfVXdt519tYPp9C452fAq64=/586x463/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YYFFTNN3BLGFC6A62OETYMRIQU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuMZKtfVXdt519tYPp9C452fAq64%3D%2F586x463%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYYFFTNN3BLGFC6A62OETYMRIQU.gif&h=20e64a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳靄儀昨指初選絕對合法，呼籲港人堅持自己投票的權力。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】公民黨昨晚舉行初<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n「行出嚟，表達我哋係唔肯認輸」。前黨魁余若薇則稱，「越驚越縮空間只會越細，越多人投票保障會越大」，寄語港人「做返平時做嘅嘢，唔好自我放棄、審查，人哋都未拉你就驚定先」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政府圖阻選民表態反惡法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰：戰鬥意志仍喺度<br />\n<br />\n循九東參加初選的立法會議員譚文豪認為，香港人現時的抗爭，「係為咗令下一代唔使抗爭」，認為國安法雖將恐懼包圍香港，但相信香港人願意互相扶持，亦不怕極權打壓：「你有鄭雁雄（國安公署署長），我哋有鄭達鴻，點解要驚你？」循港島參加初選的鄭達鴻承諾公民黨上下會與香港人同行，指民主派「35+」目標或許無法達到，但認為「未投票就認輸，就唔係香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n參與新界西初選的工黨吳敏兒昨晚也在葵芳<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n全世界知，香港人心不死，戰鬥意志仍然喺到」。"},{"pid":"70f6616b9ed36398d370a63e10b35b61b77234de","tid":2101874,"uid":242393,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raoVDRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraoVDRs.jpg&h=ae3d7cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過個人推薦投本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1582fe96076b234289cc83a8de3ad0f736eb36","tid":2101874,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f18b50c37f6602efc48f412b8e72ba03c8a12256","tid":2101874,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">全港票站一覽：</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1iZAOFKAfDIxeGdVWVoXS8-TAUJxzENpk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1iZAOFKAfDIxeGdVWVoXS8-TAUJxzENpk&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=77a31492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1iZAOFKAfDIxeGdVWVoXS8-TAUJxzENpk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5iZktG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5iZktG.png&h=c86f7eae&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xs5XRAn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXs5XRAn.jpg&h=b94cfff4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUsrK2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUsrK2M.jpg&h=89946e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">選民資料(預早截圖)：</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a9c7de73